All 17 test/test_partial.py tests pass on this branch (7 originals
+ 10 new). The new function agrees with the standard solver at
reg >= 1.0 (atol 1e-4) and stays finite at reg down to 5e-4 on a
50x50 cost-scale-~50 problem (the exact failure mode of issue #723).

The example uses MPLBACKEND=Agg-safe code so CI can render without
a display.

